info.desc: This is what the intersection looks like when facing northward.
info.instr: Go to the second floor of Williamson Hall. Make your way towards the south-most point of the building.
Enter the tunnel entrance, taking the first left (the right goes outside).
This will bring you to the first picture, you will be coming from the leftmost path, so you will take a left to the pictured center path.
There will be some stairs, and on the right an entrance to the nolte center garage.
